{"tid":527679,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"控方指首被告要求10：1後停入球","createTime":"2018-01-13T03:03:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-13T05:58:16.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b8d2454e488fe630a3c48be3ac94eb3d5509b6ac","tid":527679,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T03:03:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180113/20273128\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180113%2F20273128&d=TuyeV8xSm8Igy1rjC3vPZR4KspRE1ZdqvS7v6cf6aI4%3D&h=24ed4f7f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180113%2F20273128&h=aad52b00\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180113/20273128</a><br />\n<br />\n控方指首被告要求10：1後停入球<br />\n<br />\n法庭   <br />\n         <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180113/large/13ls3p3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180113%2Flarge%2F13ls3p3.jpg&h=5c8deb74&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n首被告郭建邦涉操控球賽。何柏佳攝<br />\n<br />\n【飛馬假波案】<br />\n【本報訊】港超聯球會香港飛馬5名前球員被指於2016年打假波案昨日開審。控方庭上提到，除前足球先生李威廉承認有份參與打假波的兩場分別於3及4月的香港飛馬對標準流浪的賽事外，早於同年2月24日一場飛馬對元朗的賽事，已出現操控球賽之事。首被告郭建邦於賽前及中途屢次向前鋒隊友黃威給予打假波指示，要求他何時入球及不要入球。<br />\n<br />\n控方在開庭陳詞指，賽前郭要求黃不要入球，並阻止元朗得分。開賽約20分鐘，郭要黃開始入球，黃其後確入了一球。至80分鐘，當時飛馬以10比1領先元朗，郭要求黃停止入球，臨完場有人要求飛馬後衞球員胡晉銘保持控球但不要入球。此時飛馬獲判十二碼，郭主射，但射失，有關比數一直維持至完場。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n前鋒賽後獲2萬元<br />\n<br />\n黃威於2月這場賽事及另一場3月對標準流浪賽事後，分別從次被告鄭禮騫和第四被告陳柏衡收到合共2萬元。<br />\n<br />\n第五被告李家豪於警誡下承認3月23日飛馬對標準流浪的賽事前接到對方後衞劉松偉來電，但他拒絕劉要求參與操控賽事，惟他確按教練李威廉指示沒盡力作賽，但稱非故意射入烏龍球。事後他從鄭收到2萬元。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：DCCC599/17<br />\n■記者蔡少玲"},{"pid":"34758d258f8e0925f036a263c335789f4b05ca70","tid":527679,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T03:20:45.000Z","msg":"爲兩萬坐監"},{"pid":"cd2294df4d04feb3c9d0ee2d88818757bfaa6ed2","tid":527679,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T03:52:01.000Z","msg":"估唔到"},{"pid":"50d602fce32ab198f683f430e0e4723322fccdb0","tid":527679,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T04:03:22.000Z","msg":"入夠唔入唔奇喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6cead217eaf0cf1db2672122b0d745447540460","tid":527679,"uid":5499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T05:03:15.000Z","msg":"10:1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8b000aa5bc3d90bdb7d811c6e20c6f1792c9401","tid":527679,"uid":161160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T05:40:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>爲兩萬坐監</blockquote><br />\n點止啊<br />\n未查到姐"},{"pid":"2997a0730ade50301a2fa4ee5d20b7869a26b681","tid":527679,"uid":73340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b8b000aa5bc3d90bdb7d811c6e20c6f1792c9401","tid":527679,"uid":161160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T05:40:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>爲兩萬坐監</blockquote><br />\n點止啊<br />\n未查到姐"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T05:58:16.000Z","msg":"至少入行到而家啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}